{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"cache-control\"><a href=\"#cache-control\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>cache-control</h2>\n<h3 id=\"http-11以上支持，给定时长（单位s），有效时使用浏览器本地缓存，可覆盖expires\"><a href=\"#http-11%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%99%E5%AE%9A%E6%97%B6%E9%95%BF%EF%BC%88%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8Ds%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E6%97%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%B5%8F%E8%A7%88%E5%99%A8%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E7%BC%93%E5%AD%98%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E8%A6%86%E7%9B%96expires\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>HTTP 1.1以上支持，给定时长（单位s），有效时使用浏览器本地缓存，可覆盖expires</h3>\n<p>请求时的缓存指令：no-cache、no-store、max-age、max-stale、min-fresh、only-if-cached\n响应消息中的指令：public、private、no-cache、no-store、no-transform、must-revalidate、proxy- revalidate、max-age</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\">\n      <pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">Cache-Control: max-age=3600, must-revalidate</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h2 id=\"expires\"><a href=\"#expires\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>expires</h2>\n<h3 id=\"给定过期的时间，有效时使用浏览器本地缓存\"><a href=\"#%E7%BB%99%E5%AE%9A%E8%BF%87%E6%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E6%97%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%B5%8F%E8%A7%88%E5%99%A8%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E7%BC%93%E5%AD%98\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>给定过期的时间，有效时使用浏览器本地缓存</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\">\n      <pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">Expires: new Date(Date.now() + 60000)</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h2 id=\"last-modified\"><a href=\"#last-modified\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>last-Modified</h2>\n<h3 id=\"设置最后修改时间。获取到if-modified-since值后，与服务器文件修改时间比较。适用静态资源文件，不适用动态化数据\"><a href=\"#%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E6%9C%80%E5%90%8E%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E3%80%82%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E5%88%B0if-modified-since%E5%80%BC%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8E%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%83%E3%80%82%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E5%8C%96%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>设置最后修改时间。获取到If-Modified-Since值后，与服务器文件修改时间比较。适用静态资源文件，不适用动态化数据</h3>\n<p>demo:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\">\n      <pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">fs.stat(filename, function (err, stat) {\n        //获取当前文件时间\n        var lastModified = stat.mtime.toUTCString();\n        if (lastModified === req.headers[&#39;if-modified-since&#39;]) {\n            res.writeHead(304, &quot;Not Modified&quot;);\n            res.end();\n        } else {\n            fs.readFile(filename, function(err, file) {\n                var lastModified = stat.mtime.toUTCString();\n                res.setHeader(&quot;Last-Modified&quot;, lastModified);\n                res.writeHead(200, &quot;Ok&quot;);\n                res.end(file);\n            });\n        }\n    });</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h2 id=\"etag\"><a href=\"#etag\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>etag</h2>\n<h3 id=\"使用hash值做标识。获取到if-none-match值后，与接口内容的hash值比较。\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8hash%E5%80%BC%E5%81%9A%E6%A0%87%E8%AF%86%E3%80%82%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E5%88%B0if-none-match%E5%80%BC%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8E%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E7%9A%84hash%E5%80%BC%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%83%E3%80%82\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>使用hash值做标识。获取到if-none-match值后，与接口内容的hash值比较。</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\">\n      <pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">var hash = crypto.createHash(&#39;md5&#39;).update(html).digest(&#39;base64&#39;);\nif(ctx.request.headers[&#39;if-none-match&#39;] == hash){\n      ctx.status = 304;\n      return;\n    }\n    ctx.set({\n      &#39;Etag&#39;: hash\n    });</code></pre>\n      </div>","timeToRead":3,"excerpt":"cache-control HTTP 1.1以上支持，给定时长（单位s），有效时使用浏览器本地缓存，可覆盖expires 请求时的缓存指令：no-cache、no-store、max-age、max-stale、min-fresh、only-if-cached…","frontmatter":{"title":"node实现页面缓存的策略","cover":null,"date":"2017-09-02T10:08:29.000Z","category":"node","tags":["node"]},"fields":{"nextTitle":"ssh管理服务器","nextSlug":"/node/server/ssh/","prevTitle":"tcp-ip","prevSlug":"/node/tcp-ip/","slug":"/node/cache/cache/","date":"2017-09-01T16:00:00.000Z"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/node/cache/cache/"}}